    <h1>Disavow</h1>
    <p class="description">A Google Search Console tool for telling Google to ignore specific backlinks when ranking your site. Reserved for <strong>manual actions, negative SEO attacks, or known-purchased links</strong> you cannot manually remove.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
